1
00:00:01,220 --> 00:00:02,400
We're going in.

2
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:05,140
Get tactical, Marines!

3
00:00:06,900 --> 00:00:10,380
You heard the man, boys! It's time for some hazard pay!

4
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:14,520
Thirty seconds out. Stand by...

5
00:00:17,980 --> 00:00:18,580
Whoa.

6
00:00:34,730 --> 00:00:35,290
Huh?

7
00:00:42,090 --> 00:00:42,650
Status!

8
00:01:01,730 --> 00:01:06,030
Sir, O'Brien's down. We lost our pilots, too.

9
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:08,070
Grab their tags and ammo.

10
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:11,170
Sarge, we better get moving.

11
00:01:11,870 --> 00:01:12,430
Agreed.

12
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:14,390
We'll find better cover in those buildings.

13
00:01:15,630 --> 00:01:17,050
Butkus, you take point.

14
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:40,440
Hello!

15
00:01:42,020 --> 00:01:43,440
Sniper, third floor left.

16
00:01:43,780 --> 00:01:46,980
Here, let me give him my welcome-to-Earth gift basket.

17
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:18,620
Here, see what I have?

18
00:02:18,620 --> 00:02:19,480
Damn! Where is he?

19
00:02:27,440 --> 00:02:28,320
Anybody see him?

20
00:02:34,860 --> 00:02:36,920
Well, I'm not sure about that.

21
00:02:37,100 --> 00:02:38,580
I'm not sure of anything.

22
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:40,240
How are you, O'Brien?

23
00:02:41,480 --> 00:02:44,080
I'm not very well, sir...

24
00:02:44,080 --> 00:02:44,720
Nobody on the scene?

25
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:44,740
We'll take a short walk around.

26
00:02:44,740 --> 00:02:45,680
Take him, guys!

27
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,260
Cook the bastard.

28
00:02:55,620 --> 00:02:58,360
Second squad, this is Cortana. What is your status? Over.

29
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:01,780
We're operational, ma'am. Barely. Our pilots didn't make it.

30
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:04,460
Find a hole. Stay put. We'll come to you.

